node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Anne on August 23, 2021 tagging @harrystyles, @matty_selley, @elladeannemurray, @benselleymusic, @dee_selley, @larissachiaraselley, @gemmastyles, @mikey_selley, @angelikaselley, and @selleyjohn. May be an image of 2 people and indoor.

node.text: My heart is broken once more … our family has been reeling from the loss of our Dad / Grandad / brother / friend 💔. Dad you were so brave and courageous, always smiling and with a sharp and witty comment at just the right time. We love you totally and forever. Sleep sweetly you beautifully man. Go be with Mum 🥰 xxx THANK YOU EVERYONE FOR YOUR THOUGHTS & COMMENTS XXX
